title: [Progressive Rock] [2015] [MP3@320] UnderwaterJive - Wake Up
description:
UnderwaterJive - Wake Up
----
ProgressiveAlternative Rock band, The band have created a unique signature sound, combining Ambient and ethnical elements. The album creates an abstract picture of the human inner self, regrets, and dreams. the main character is in a search for his truth, inside his past memories. This is the bands 1st album.
